description: 2 Fat 2 Fly was founded by Ramone and Corey with the vision of saving the world from boring, plain chicken wings by stuffing ACTUAL FOOD inside of them. No, seriously, these guys take 100% jumbo, bone-in chicken wings and stuff them with the most glorious combination of treats you can imagine. (What types of treats you ask? Check out our menu for all of the fun and delicious flavors!)As the teams right and left "wings", Joey and Sean joined 2 Fat 2 Fly a few year after the inception of the wing-revolution.This dedicated group of young entrepreneurs will. not. rest. until every mouth has tasted these stuffed chicken wings.
name: 2 Fat 2 Fly
